"1a04a2d\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-73eb6eb\" data-id=\"73eb6eb\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac855f7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ac855f7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Vickie Boozer has enjoyed a successful career in residential real estate in Texas since 1996. She has over 250 happy clients, and has represented more than 30 of those clients in multiple transactions. She is dedicated to providing first class service to all of her clients. Approximately 95% of her business comes from repeat clients and personal referrals. Vickie works with buyers and sellers with all levels of experience, from first-time home buyers and sellers to the savviest investor. She especially enjoys working all over Austin and surrounding areas, and has a wide range of market knowledge to assist her clients in finding the ideal location.<br \/><br \/>Vickie has a background in technology development, and she enjoys bringing that knowledge to her real estate business, using the latest technologies to be more efficient and save time for herself and her clients.<br \/><br \/>Vickie is a Certified Residential Specialist (CRS), being one of only 3% of all Realtors\u00ae nationwide holding this credential. She is also an Accredited Buyer Representative (ABR), a Graduate of the Real Estate Institute (GRI), and an e-PRO technology professional. She is a member of the Austin Board of Realtors\u00ae, the Texas Association of Realtors\u00ae, the National Association of Realtors\u00ae, the Real Estate Buyer\u2019s Agency Council, and the Council of Residential Specialists.<br \/><br \/>In her spare time Vickie enjoys spending time with her husband of 30 years, her daughter Allison, and her English Springer Spaniel, Jean-Luc. She also manages a personal vacation rental property on the Gulf coast of Alabama. She loves Austin, the beautiful Texas Hill Country, and the Highland Lakes, and spends as much time as possible seeing the sites around Austin, especially all of the great Austin music venues. She is an avid music fan and loves going to concerts, and also enjoys travel, cooking, gardening and Yoga.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac11626 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"ac11626\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<style>\n.elementor-column.elementor-col-33 ul.elementor-icon-list-items {\n    padding-bottom: 10px;\n}    \n<\/style>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Our Agents Vickie Boozer Sales Associate Contact Vickie Boozer has enjoyed a successful career in residential real estate in Texas since 1996. She has over 250 happy clients, and has represented more than 30 of those clients in multiple transactions. She is dedicated to providing first class service to all of her clients. Approximately 95% [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"elementor_header_footer","meta":{"_vp_format_video_url":"","_vp_image_focal_point":[],"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-3776","page","type-page","status-publish",